    "readme": "\u003ch1\u003e\u003ca id=\"user-content-drp-spack-config\" class=\"anchor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"#drp-spack-config\"\u003e\u003cspan aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003edrp-spack-config\u003c/h1\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCCI DRP Spack configuration\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch1\u003e\u003ca id=\"user-content-contents\" class=\"anchor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"#contents\"\u003e\u003cspan aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003econtents\u003c/h1\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eopenFoam24 - spack environment for an OpenFoam Organization 2.4.0 install\u003c/p\u003e\n",
